on BabyLift\" (Trieu), 176 \"Opposing Forces\" (Ruiz-Perilla), 114 Osian, Nkem, 268 out-of-the-ordinary events, 31–33 ``` ``` \"Outdoor School\" (Shambry), 103 outlines, 16, 72 \"Outrunning the Dark\" (Seppilu), 177 \"Over the Bridge\" (Banks), 93 P Pang, Aaron, 33 Park, Dylan, 232 \"Past Wasn't Done with Me, The\" (Powers), 189 \"Patriots Game, The\" (Al Abdullatif), 188 \"Perfect Circle, A\" (Johnstone), 176–177 perspective, 124, 131–132, 152, 220–221, 316 shifts in, 35–38, 67 Pillitteri, Carl, 161–163, 164, 207–208 Ping, Wang, 186 pitching new stories, 60, 303–304, 309–310 point of view, 69, 100, 168.",
