  {
    "id": "How to Tell a Story_sem_1",
    "title": "GOOD LUCK!",
    "section": "It must be ON THEME.",
    "source": "How to Tell a Story",
    "text": "Repeat stories. Stereotypes. Confessions. Gratuitous anything. (SEE MOTH DON'T LIST.) What we do want: Hook us in.",
