    "text": "ion\" (Conover), 36 \"Kind of Wisdom, A\" (Lee), 61, 68, 258–259 King, Martin Luther, Jr., 266 King, Mary-Claire, 9, 34 \"Kirk's Christmas Gift\" (Cooper), 83 Klutse, Marina, 111, 276 Koch, Ed, 203–205 ``` ``` Kucha, Abeny, 158 Kumanyika, Chenjerai, xvii–xxiii, 45 L Lacayo, Alfonso, 112, 120–121 Lakshmi, Padma, xiii–xv, 90 Lane, Faye, 18 last and first lines of stories, 180–181, 189–190, 197 \"Leaving Baghdad\" (Mousa), 189 Lee, Ellie, 60–61, 68, 258–259 Lee, Jen, 18 Legiardi-Laura, Roland, 8 Leonardo, Shaun, 88–89 lens, 68–69, 164–168, 220–221, 242, 281, 310 Lepelstat, David, 180 \"Let It Go\" (Lepelstat), 180 Levenstein, Victor, 176 \"Life After Death\" (Echols), 139 \"Life Support\" (Summerville), 188 ``` ``` \"Life Web Exercise,\" 252 listening, 11–12, 50, 101, 115, 253, 272–279 lists, 29, 31 Litt, David, 56 \"Little Pink General Lee, The\" (James), 242–243 Little Red Riding Hood, 167–168 Lombardi, George, 106–107 M Mahl, Nancy, 176 main event, 84–85, 104–107, 160–163, 189, 270 \"Making Moves\" (Ashley), 275–276 \"Man and Beast\" (Rabinowitz), 159–160 Mandela, Nelson, 64–65 Marin, Cheech, 275 Martel, Jay, 63 Maseno, Bina, 177 Massimino, Michael, 47–48 \"Maybe\" (Williamson), 121 ``` ``` McBride, Christian, 92, 226 McCourt, Frank, 8 McDaniels, Darryl \"DMC,\" 102, 225–226 McNally, Megan, 42–43 \"Meeting Miles\" (Collier), 117 \"Meeting Nelson Mandela\" (Jantjies), 63–65 Melvin, Leland, 87–88 memories mining for, 27–49 unreliability of, 96–97, 99 memorization, 195–197 \"Met, Mrs.",
