    "text": "list](http://themoth.org/storyplaylist) for a playlist of the stories featured in this book. We hope they will inspire you to share a few of your own!\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:SKIP -->\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n# <span id=\"page-356-0\"></span>HOW TO TELL A STORY\n\nMEG BOWLES, CATHERINE BURNS, JENIFER HIXSON, SARAH AUSTIN JENNESS, AND KATE TELLERS\n\n\nA BOOK CLUB GUIDE\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->",
    "char_count": 384,
