    "text": "nal opportunity to laugh and cry with strangers. She was the intern that edited the podcast on GarageBand.\n\nInstagram: [@thekatetellers](http://instagram.com/thekatetellers)\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n# Available from THE MOTH\n\n\n\"Stories that attest to . . . the shared threads of love, loss, fear and kindness that connect us.\"\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->",
    "char_count": 356,
