    "text": "and more, available on our website.\n\nJoin our online book club community!\n\ngrandomhousebookclub.com\n\nRandom House Book Club\n\nBecause Stories Are Better Shared\n\nRANDOM HOUSE\n\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n# Wat's next on your reading list?\n\n[Discover](http://links.penguinrandomhouse.com/type/prhebooklanding/isbn/9780593139011/display/1) your next great read!\n\nGet personalized book picks and up-to-date news about this author.\n\nSign up [now.](http://links.penguinrandomhouse.com/type/prhebooklanding/isbn/9780593139011/display/2)\n\n\n*Your gateway to knowledge and culture. Accessible for everyone.*\n\n\n[z-library.sk](https://z-library.sk/) [z-lib.gs](https://z-lib.gs/) [z-lib.fm](https://z-lib.fm/) [go-to-library.sk](https://go-to-library.sk/)\n\n\nOffi[cial Telegram channel](https://t.me/zlibrary_official)\n\n\n[Z-Access](https://go-to-library.sk/)\n\n\n<https://wikipedia.org/wiki/Z-Library>",
