  {
    "id": "How to Tell a Story_54e4b4e1",
    "title": "NEW YORK TIMES BESTSELLER",
    "section": "NEW YORK TIMES BESTSELLER",
    "source": "How to Tell a Story",
    "text": "<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n# NEW YORK TIMES BESTSELLER\n\nTHE ESSENTIAL GUIDE to MEMORABLE STORYTELLING from **THE MOTH**\n\nH O W\n\n\nTOTELL\n\n\nASTORY\n\n\nMEG BOWLES, CATHERINE BURNS, JENIFER HIXSON,\n\nSARAH AUSTIN JENNESS, and KATE TELLERS\n\nForeword by PADMA LAKSHMI Introduction by CHENJERAI KUMANYIKA\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n# **Praise for** *How to Tell a Story*\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->",
