    "text": "ON,\n\nSARAH AUSTIN JENNESS, and KATE TELLERS\n\nForeword by PADMA LAKSHMI Introduction by CHENJERAI KUMANYIKA\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n# **Praise for** *How to Tell a Story*\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n#### **A** *New York Times* **and Indiebound bestseller**\n\n\"Inspiring…provides everything readers need to share their own personal narratives.\"",
