  {
    "id": "How to Tell a Story_f83a3a09",
    "title": "[Chapter 11: The Ripple Effect](#page-261-0)",
    "section": "[Chapter 11: The Ripple Effect](#page-261-0)",
    "source": "How to Tell a Story",
    "text": "-240-0)\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n#### *[Nerves](#page-243-0) [Who Is Your Audience?](#page-251-0)*\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n# [Part 4: The Power of Story](#page-260-0)\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->\n\n# [Chapter 11: The Ripple Effect](#page-261-0)\n\n*[Stories in School](#page-261-1)*\n\n*[Stories at Work](#page-267-0)*\n\n*[Stories with Family](#page-272-0)*\n\n*[Stories in the World](#page-278-0)*\n\n<!-- BOUNDARY:CONTENT -->",
